ck|first=Gail T.|date=2002-11-11|url=https://www.amazon.com/The-Life-Benjamin-Banneker-African-American/dp/0938420593/ref%3Dcm_cr_pr_product_top?ie=UTF8|title=Benjamin Banneker \u2013 the man and the myths|work=Customer review of Bedini, Silvio A. (1999). \"The Life of Benjamin Banneker: The First African-American Man of Science\", 2nd ed., Baltimore: Maryland Historical Society |publisher=Amazon.com|accessdate=2017-03-18|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310095152/http://www.amazon.com/The-Life-Benjamin-Banneker-African-American/dp/0938420593#customerReviews|archivedate=2016-03-10}} \n** {{cite journal|last=Toscano|first=Patrick|date=March 2000|url=https://archives.profsurv.com/magazine/article.aspx?i=567|title=Book Review: Bedini, Silvio A. (1999), \"The Life of Benjamin Banneker: The First African-American Man of Science\", 2nd ed., Baltimore: Maryland Historical Society|journal=Professional Surveyor Magazine|volume=20|number=3|location=[[Frederick, Maryland]]|publisher=Flatdog Media, Inc.|accessdate=2019-09-12|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912002204/https://archives.profsurv.com/magazine/article.aspx?i=567|archivedate=2019-09-12}}\n* {{cite web|last=Bedini|first=Silvio A.|editor1-first=Charles Coulston |editor1-last=Gillispie|editor2-first=Frederic Lawrence|editor2-last=Holmes|editor3-first=Noretta|editor3-last=Koertge|url=http://www.encyclopedia.com/topic/Benjamin_Banneker.aspx|title=Banneker, Benjamin|work=[[Dictionary of Scientific Biography|Complete Dictionary of Scientific Biography]]|year=2008|isbn=\t9780684315591|oclc=187313311|location=[[Detroit, Michigan]]|publisher=[[Charles Scribner's Sons]]; [[Cengage|Boston, Massachusetts: CENGAGE]]|via=[[Encyclopedia.com]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180223234416/https://www.encyclopedia.com/people/science-and-technology/mathematics-biographies/benjamin-banneker|archivedate=2018-02-23|accessdate=March 16, 2020}}\n* {{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/we