y cool' way to end film franchise |website=EW|access-date=June 25, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://variety.com/2019/film/news/purge-5-director-everardo-gout-mars-1203288438/|title=Next 'Purge' Installment Finds Director in 'Mars' Helmer (EXCLUSIVE)|date=August 1, 2019|website=Variety|access-date=August 2, 2019}}</ref>\n| distributed by [[Universal Pictures]]\n|-\n| October 16, 2020\n| ''[[Halloween Kills]]''\n| distributed by Universal Pictures; co-production with [[Miramax]], Rough House Pictures and [[Compass International Pictures|Trancas International Pictures]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://collider.com/halloween-2-release-date-jamie-lee-curtis/|title=Exclusive: 'Halloween 2' Gearing Up for Fall Shoot, 2020 Release; Jamie Lee Curtis to Return|last=Sneider|first=Jeff|date=June 20, 2019|website=[[Collider (website)|Collider]]|accessdate=July 13, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| March 19, 2021\n| ''[[Paranormal Activity: The Ghost Dimension#Sequel|Paranormal Activity 7]]''<ref>{{cite news|last=McNary|first=Dave|url=https://variety.com/2019/film/news/paramount-blumhouse-seventh-paranormal-activity-movie-1203248018/|title=Paramount, Blumhouse Announce Seventh ''Paranormal Activity'' Movie|website=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|date=June 19, 2019|accessdate=August 4, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://collider.com/paranormal-activity-7-release-date-2021/|title=Paramount Sets a ''Paranormal Activity 7'' Release Date for 2021|website=[[Collider (website)|Collider]]|last=Lawrence|first=Gregory|date=November 8, 2019|accessdate=December 31, 2019}}</ref>\n| distributed by [[Paramount Pictures]]\n|-\n| October 15, 2021 \n| ''[[Halloween Kills#Sequel|Halloween Ends]]''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://twitter.com/jamieleecurtis/status/1152271317682364416|title=\u201cIt ain\u2019t over till the fat lady sings.\u201d Well, my friends and fans....I\u2019m just WARMING UP Happy Halloween 2020/2021 @halloweenmovie #halloweenkills #halloweenendspic.twitter.com/mjkZNdYqiY|last=Curtis|first