uary  4, 2020\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |''Final Cuts: New Tales of Hollywood Horror and Other Spectacles''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |Various Artists\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |June 2, 2020\n|-\n|}\n\n===Comics===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|- style=\"background:#b0c4de; text-align:center;\"\n! Year\n! Comic\n! Writer\n! Release date\n! Notes\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center\" |2017\n| style=\"text-align:center\" |''[[Sleight]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center\" |Ryan Parrott \n| style=\"text-align:center\" |March 30, 2017\n| Tie-in [[prequel]] [[comic]] to ''Sleight'' (2017)\n|-\n|}\n\n==Podcasts==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|- style=\"background:#b0c4de; text-align:center;\"\n! Year\n! Podcast\n! Host(s)\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |2016\u2013present\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |''Shock Waves''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |Rob Galluzzo, Elric Kane<br>[[Rebekah McKendry]], Ryan Turek\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |2018\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |''Post Mortem with Mick Garris''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |[[Mick Garris]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" style=\"text-align:center;\" |2018\u2014present\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |''Fear Initiative''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |Clarke Wolfe, Morgan Peter Brown, Cara Mandel,<br>Josh Forbes, [[Megan Duffy (actress)|Megan Duffy]], Jeff Seidman,<br>David Ian McKendry, [[Rob Schrab]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |''Attack of the Queerwolf!''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |Michael Kennedy, [[M.A. Fortin]]<br>Nay Bever, Brennan Klein\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |''[[The Oval Office Tapes]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |[[R. J. Cutler]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |2020\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |''The Mantawauk Caves''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |[[Dan Bush]]\n|-\n|}\n\n==See also==\n* [[Blumhouse Productions]]\n* [[Jason Blum]]\n* [[Monkeypaw Productions]]\n* [[Platinum Dunes]]\n* [[Ghost House Pictures]]\n* [[Blinding Edge Pictures